      "title": "Goat",
      "pageid": 1907,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Goat\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 5px;\"><img alt=\"Goat.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/5/52/Goat.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"84\" height=\"75\" />\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic;\">Happy adults provide goat milk every other day. A milk pail is required to harvest the milk.  Lives in the barn.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Information\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Building\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Big Barn.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/81/Big_Barn.png/24px-Big_Barn.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/81/Big_Barn.png/36px-Big_Barn.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/8/81/Big_Barn.png/48px-Big_Barn.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Big Barn</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Purchase Price\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"4000 \"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />4,000g</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Produce\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Goat Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/45/Goat_Milk.png/24px-Goat_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/45/Goat_Milk.png/36px-Goat_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/45/Goat_Milk.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Goat_Milk\" title=\"Goat Milk\">Goat Milk</a></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Large Goat Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png/24px-Large_Goat_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png/36px-Large_Goat_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Large_Goat_Milk\" title=\"Large Goat Milk\">Large Goat Milk</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p>The <b>Goat</b> is an <a href=\"/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">animal</a> that lives in a <a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Big Barn</a>. Goats can be purchased at <a href=\"/Marnie%27s_Ranch\" title=\"Marnie&#39;s Ranch\">Marnie's Ranch</a> for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"4000\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />4,000g</span>. Goats can become pregnant and give <a href=\"/Animals#Animal_Births\" title=\"Animals\">birth</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Produce\">Produce</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Goat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Produce\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>Main article: <a href=\"/Animals#Produce\" title=\"Animals\">Animals#Produce</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>Goats who eat every day mature after 5 nights have passed. A mature and fed goat produces <a href=\"/Goat_Milk\" title=\"Goat Milk\">Goat Milk</a> every 2 days. Once sufficient <a href=\"/Animals#Friendship\" title=\"Animals\">friendship</a> and happiness are reached, they will produce <a href=\"/Large_Goat_Milk\" title=\"Large Goat Milk\">Large Goat Milk</a>. Goat Milk can be collected using a <a href=\"/Milk_Pail\" title=\"Milk Pail\">Milk Pail</a>. Milking a goat by hand increases friendship by 5 points. Alternatively, an <a href=\"/Auto-Grabber\" title=\"Auto-Grabber\">Auto-Grabber</a> will automatically milk every Goat in a Barn.\n</p><p>Goat Milk can be placed in a <a href=\"/Cheese_Press\" title=\"Cheese Press\">Cheese Press</a> to produce <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a>, which sells for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"400\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />400g</span> or <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"600\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />600g</span> depending on quality.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Image\n</th>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<th>Description\n</th>\n<th>Sell Price\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Goat_Milk.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Goat Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/4/45/Goat_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Goat_Milk\" title=\"Goat Milk\">Goat Milk</a>\n</td>\n<td>The milk of a goat.\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r146727\">.mw-parser-output .parent,.mw-parser-output .backimage,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent{position:relative;top:0;left:0}.mw-parser-output .backimage img,.mw-parser-output .foreimage img,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{display:block}.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{opacity:0.6}.mw-parser-output .foreimage{position:absolute;bottom:0;right:0}</style><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Goat Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/45/Goat_Milk.png/24px-Goat_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/45/Goat_Milk.png/36px-Goat_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/45/Goat_Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>225g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Goat Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/45/Goat_Milk.png/24px-Goat_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/45/Goat_Milk.png/36px-Goat_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/45/Goat_Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Silver Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>281g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Goat Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/45/Goat_Milk.png/24px-Goat_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/45/Goat_Milk.png/36px-Goat_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/45/Goat_Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>337g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Goat Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/45/Goat_Milk.png/24px-Goat_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/45/Goat_Milk.png/36px-Goat_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/45/Goat_Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Iridium Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>450g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Large_Goat_Milk.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Large Goat Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Large_Goat_Milk\" title=\"Large Goat Milk\">Large Goat Milk</a>\n</td>\n<td>A gallon of creamy goat's milk.\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Large Goat Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png/24px-Large_Goat_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png/36px-Large_Goat_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>345g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Large Goat Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png/24px-Large_Goat_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png/36px-Large_Goat_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Silver Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>431g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Large Goat Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png/24px-Large_Goat_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png/36px-Large_Goat_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>517g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Large Goat Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png/24px-Large_Goat_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png/36px-Large_Goat_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f2/Large_Goat_Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Iridium Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>690g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Reproduction\">Reproduction</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Goat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Reproduction\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Goats, like <a href=\"/Cow\" title=\"Cow\">cows</a>, <a href=\"/Sheep\" title=\"Sheep\">sheep</a>, and <a href=\"/Pig\" title=\"Pig\">pigs</a>, have a low chance to reproduce. The more animals there are inside the same <a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">barn</a>, the higher the chance an animal will give birth.\nWhen it occurs, the player will receive a notice at the bottom of the screen before the day starts, stating \"During the night, [parent's name] gave birth to a baby goat.\" Other than this, there is no indication that a goat is pregnant.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selling\">Selling</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Goat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Selling\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Goats can be sold. The <a href=\"/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">selling price</a> is dependent on how many <a href=\"/Friendship\" title=\"Friendship\">hearts</a> the animal has (<span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"5200\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />5,200g</span> max).\n</p><p>To sell a coop or barn animal, right-click the animal after petting. The friendship/mood interface appears. Move the cursor over the gold coin button at the right to see how much you can sell the animal for. Click that button and the confirmation that follows to complete the sale.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">Animals</a> and Produce\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Coop</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Chicken\" title=\"Chicken\">Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Brown Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Brown Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Dinosaur\" title=\"Dinosaur\">Dinosaur</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Dinosaur_Egg\" title=\"Dinosaur Egg\">Dinosaur Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Duck\" title=\"Duck\">Duck</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Duck_Egg\" title=\"Duck Egg\">Duck Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Duck_Feather\" title=\"Duck Feather\">Duck Feather</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Golden_Chicken\" title=\"Golden Chicken\">Golden Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Golden_Egg\" title=\"Golden Egg\">Golden Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Rabbit\" title=\"Rabbit\">Rabbit</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a> • <a href=\"/Rabbit%27s_Foot\" title=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot\">Rabbit's Foot</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Void_Chicken\" title=\"Void Chicken\">Void Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Void_Egg\" title=\"Void Egg\">Void Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Barn</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cow\" title=\"Cow\">Cow</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Milk\" title=\"Milk\">Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Milk\" title=\"Large Milk\">Large Milk</a>)</sup> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Goat</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Goat_Milk\" title=\"Goat Milk\">Goat Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Goat_Milk\" title=\"Large Goat Milk\">Large Goat Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Sheep\" title=\"Sheep\">Sheep</a>  <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Ostrich\" title=\"Ostrich\">Ostrich</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Pig\" title=\"Pig\">Pig</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Truffle\" title=\"Truffle\">Truffle</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Fish\" title=\"Fish\">Fish</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Roe\" title=\"Roe\">Roe</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Slime_Hutch\" title=\"Slime Hutch\">Slime Hutch</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Slimes\" title=\"Slimes\">Slimes</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Slime\" title=\"Slime\">Slime</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Ball\" title=\"Slime Ball\">Slime Ball</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Egg\" title=\"Slime Egg\">Slime Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Other\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Cat</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Dog</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Horse\" title=\"Animals\">Horse</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Additional_Pets\" title=\"Animals\">Turtle</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414112710\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.135 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.160 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 4004/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 16289/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1527/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4904/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.007/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 740 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  115.657      1 -total\n 54.18%   62.664      1 Template:Infobox_animal\n 45.21%   52.286      3 Template:Description\n 31.16%   36.039      2 Template:Qualityprice\n 13.02%   15.064      3 Template:Name\n  9.37%   10.837      8 Template:Overlayimg\n  3.12%    3.614      5 Template:Price\n  1.33%    1.542      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n  1.24%    1.436      1 Template:Main_article\n  1.12%    1.294      1 Template:NavboxAnimals\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:1907-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414112710 and revision id 190212\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox animal\n|image    = Goat.png\n|buyprice = 4000\n|building = {{Name|Big Barn}}\n|produce  = {{Name|Goat Milk}}{{Name|Large Goat Milk}}\n}}\nThe '''Goat''' is an [[Animals|animal]] that lives in a [[Barn|Big Barn]]. Goats can be purchased at [[Marnie's Ranch]] for {{Price|4000}}. Goats can become pregnant and give [[Animals#Animal Births|birth]].\n\n==Produce==\n{{main article|Animals#Produce}}\nGoats who eat every day mature after 5 nights have passed. A mature and fed goat produces [[Goat Milk]] every 2 days. Once sufficient [[Animals#Friendship|friendship]] and happiness are reached, they will produce [[Large Goat Milk]]. Goat Milk can be collected using a [[Milk Pail]]. Milking a goat by hand increases friendship by 5 points. Alternatively, an [[Auto-Grabber]] will automatically milk every Goat in a Barn.\n\nGoat Milk can be placed in a [[Cheese Press]] to produce [[Goat Cheese]], which sells for {{Price|400}} or {{Price|600}} depending on quality.\n\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Sell Price\n|-\n|[[File:Goat Milk.png]]\n|[[Goat Milk]]\n|{{Description|Goat Milk}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Goat Milk|225|dsv=false}}\n|-\n|[[File:Large Goat Milk.png]]\n|[[Large Goat Milk]]\n|{{Description|Large Goat Milk}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Large Goat Milk|345|dsv=false}}\n|}\n\n==Reproduction==\nGoats, like [[cow]]s, [[sheep]], and [[pig]]s, have a low chance to reproduce. The more animals there are inside the same [[barn]], the higher the chance an animal will give birth.\nWhen it occurs, the player will receive a notice at the bottom of the screen before the day starts, stating \"During the night, [parent's name] gave birth to a baby goat.\" Other than this, there is no indication that a goat is pregnant.\n\n==Selling==\nGoats can be sold. The [[gold|selling price]] is dependent on how many [[Friendship|hearts]] the animal has ({{Price|5200}} max).\n\nTo sell a coop or barn animal, right-click the animal after petting. The friendship/mood interface appears. Move the cursor over the gold coin button at the right to see how much you can sell the animal for. Click that button and the confirmation that follows to complete the sale.\n\n{{NavboxAnimals}}\n\n[[Category:Barn animals]]\n\n[[de:Ziege]]\n[[es:Cabra]]\n[[fr:Chèvre]]\n[[it:Capra]]\n[[ja:ヤギ]]\n[[ko:염소]]\n[[hu:Kecske]]\n[[pt:Cabra]]\n[[ru:Коза]]\n[[tr:Keçi]]\n[[zh:山羊]]"
